languages.text:
The {g|Encyclopedia:FlagshipSpace}flagship{/g} makes a shallow warp jump in a forward direction.
When the flagship jumps through a unit, that unit suffers <u>((from 25 to 35)% of its maximum {g|Encyclopedia:HullIntegritySpace}hull integrity{/g})</u> warp {g|Encyclopedia:SpaceBattleDamageGlossary}damage{/g}.
<indent=5%>Range: 5 cells.</indent>
<indent=5%>Cooldown: <u>(from 1 to 3)</u> rounds at random.</indent>

{g|Encyclopedia:FlagshipSpace}旗舰{/g}朝前进方向进行浅层亚空间跳跃。
若旗舰穿过了敌方单位，则该单位会受到亚空间{g|Encyclopedia:SpaceBattleDamageGlossary}伤害{/g}，等同于<u>最大{g|Encyclopedia:HullIntegritySpace}舰体完整度{/g}的25%到35%</u>。
<indent=5%>射程：5格。</indent>
<indent=5%>冷却时间：随机<u>一到三轮</u>。</indent>
